5
00:00:03,160 --> 00:00:04,440
Sin un arañazo.

6
00:00:04,440 --> 00:00:05,000
En la acera.

7
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Así, sin más.

8
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:06,720
Al final vais a ver

9
